Packages 
Package Description
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app
This package includes all source code of this application.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.activities
This package has all activities for the app.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.api
This package implements the connection to the api of the backend.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.api.domain
Implements the Model of the backend
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.api.rest
Clients implementing the REST API of Backend.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.data
This package combines the api with the app model and implements the cache.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.data.cache
Package holds the cache of api responses.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.fragments
This package includes all fragments.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.fragments.findRoutes
This package shows a fragments, where you can find a route.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.fragments.friends
This package shows all friends in a list and gives the chance to add some.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.fragments.navigationdrawer
This package shows the user profil fragment.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.fragments.routes
This package shows a route fragment and fitting adapter.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.fragments.single
This package displaying information on a single track or a route.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.fragments.tracks
This package shows all own drives/tracks including the fitting adapter.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.modell
This package is the model of this application.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.modell.assembler
This package holds classes to convert between api model and app model.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.router
The classes in this package are used to route over a given track.
edu.hm.cs.bikebattle.app.tracker
This package implements the tracking function.
